I'm a burger snob and these are Ahhhhmazing!  These burgers are huge, thick, juicy and perfectly done to your taste. And the bun - a perfectly soft brioche that melds into the burger.   They have many menu options at a great price, especially on happy hour.  And, if you like shakes (which I know doesn't help our diets) but they're loaded with the extras (brownie bites in chocolate and Nilla wafers in the Vanilla).    I can't wait to go back for more!  Hopefully, the District enters into the Burger Battle during Culinary Festival - definite winner!

