We loved it!  I bought the First in Line Fast pass at $20pp - just get the regular $10 fast past.  The lines are long at the haunted houses, which I thought were totally scary!  The Zombie paint ball truck was fun to us as well, but the guns are attached to the truck.  I was on the left side and thought the right had more targets, yet we all ended at the same time, so I think that's perception and they're probably even.  On three people, we spent a lot of money on the tix and was in/out in an hour ready to go to another haunted house.  Overall, I loved it but probably wouldn't shell out that much money next time.  We did have a blast!

